OL,3,CTributes to 'kind and gentle'
OL,4,Cuniversity student stabbed to death in
OL,5,CBristol
OL,7,FA family has paid tribute to a "kind
OL,8,Fand gentle" university student who was
OL,9,Fstabbed to death in Bristol.
OL,11,FRobotics student Jamie Collins, 21,
OL,12,Fwas found dead in the garden of an
OL,13,Faddress on Cleve Road, Filton, in the
OL,14,Fearly hours of Thursday 9 April.
OL,16,FFellow university student Zack
OL,17,FCoughlan, 23, has been charged with
OL,18,Fmurdering Jamie, who he lived with as
OL,19,Fpart of a student house share.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
