FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1776435066
OL,3,CTributes to 'kind and gentle'
OL,4,Cuniversity student stabbed to death in
OL,5,CBristol
OL,7,FIn a tribute, the Collins family said:
OL,8,F"Words cannot describe how we are
OL,9,Ffeeling as a family right now. Our
OL,10,FJamie was a bright, kind, gentle and
OL,11,Funassuming young man with his whole
OL,12,Flife ahead of him.
OL,14,F"He was looking forward to finishing
OL,15,Fhis Uni journey and planning to come
OL,16,Fhome to us in Swansea in just a few
OL,17,Fweeks' time.
OL,19,F"We know he was heading for a hugely
OL,20,Fsuccessful future following his
OL,21,Fengineering and robotics degree.
OL,26,@pD@AOUvD@AOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1776435066
OL,3,CTributes to 'kind and gentle'
OL,4,Cuniversity student stabbed to death in
OL,5,CBristol
OL,7,F"We are continuing to work with and be
OL,8,Fsupported by Avon and Somerset Police
OL,9,Fat this excruciating time.
OL,11,F"The outpouring of love and support
OL,12,Ffrom Jamie's friends and ours has been
OL,13,Fcompletely overwhelming and we would
OL,14,Flike to thank everyone for their kind
OL,15,Fmessages while we continue to grieve
OL,16,Fprivately."
OL,18,FThe family has asked for their privacy
OL,19,Fto be respected as they come to terms
OL,20,Fwith their devastating loss.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUxD@KO]
