OL,3,CTributes to 'kind and gentle'
OL,4,Cuniversity student stabbed to death in
OL,5,CBristol
OL,7,FZack Coughlan appeared at Bristol
OL,8,FCrown Court today and has been
OL,9,Fremanded in custody ahead of his next
OL,10,Fappearance.
